Title: 18 oz Child-Resistant Glass Jars (24 Pack) – Airtight, Odor-Proof Cannabis Packaging with Black Lids
Body (HTML):
Elevate your cannabis packaging with our 18 oz Child-Resistant Glass Jars, featuring sleek black lids and a secure, childproof twist mechanism. Each jar is constructed from Grade A pharmaceutical glass—ensuring professional presentation and maximum product preservation. Dispensary owners and producers will appreciate the airtight, moisture-resistant, and odor-proof design, which expertly maintains the freshness, potency, and aroma of your flower or dry bud medication.

Key Benefits & Features

  • Child-Resistant Compliance: Meet regulatory standards with a childproof cap and polyethylene foam liner designed for safe cannabis storage.
  • High-Quality Pharmaceutical Glass: Durable, scratch-resistant material highlights product quality while maintaining a clean, upscale look.
  • Airtight & Odor-Proof Seal: Prevents unwanted smells and moisture leaks to keep your cannabis fresh and potent.
  • Generous Capacity: Holds up to 28 grams of flower or dry bud—ideal for medical or recreational dispensaries.
  • Sleek Black Lid: Create a professional, discreet branding aesthetic and streamline your packaging design.
  • Convenient Bulk Pack: Includes 24 jars per case, perfect for maintaining consistent inventory and meeting increased demand.

Why Choose Our 18 oz Child-Resistant Glass Jars?

  1. Regulatory Compliance: Confidently comply with state and local laws regarding child-resistant cannabis packaging.
  2. Premium Presentation: Glass jars not only protect your products but also convey a sense of quality and trust to your customers.
  3. Extended Shelf Life: The airtight seal helps retain the cannabinoids and terpenes for longer, ensuring customers receive a fresh and potent product.
  4. Efficiency & Value: Purchasing jars in a 24-pack saves you time and money in the long run by reducing frequent re-orders.

Product Specifications

  • Material: Grade A pharmaceutical glass
  • Capacity: 18 oz (up to 28 grams of flower/dry bud)
  • Dimensions:
    • Height: 4.5 inches
    • Mouth Diameter: 2.7 inches
    • Base Diameter: 3.3 inches
  • Lid: Screw cap with child-resistant twist mechanism + polyethylene foam liner
  • Quantity: 24 jars per case
  • Color: Clear glass jar, black lid (caps come on jars)

Additional Information & Usage Tips

  • Perfect for Branding: Customize the jars with labels or stickers to match your dispensary’s branding and highlight product details.
  • Optimal Storage: For best results, store jars in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight to help maintain the quality of your cannabis products.
  • Multi-Purpose: Though ideal for cannabis flower or buds, these jars can also hold edibles, topicals, or even non-cannabis goods requiring odor-proof containers.

 

Ready to upgrade your dispensary’s packaging game? Order your 24-pack of 18 oz Child-Resistant Glass Jars today and experience premium product presentation, airtight security, and confidence in regulatory compliance—all in one sleek solution.

Title: 116mm Opaque Child Resistant Tube | Secure & Eco-Friendly Cannabis Packaging
Body (HTML):
Looking for a sustainable, user-friendly way to store and protect your cannabis products? Our 116mm Opaque Child Resistant Tube checks all the boxes. Perfect for eco-conscious consumers, these tubes feature a hinged lid that pops open with just a gentle squeeze—no twisting or pushing required.

Designed to keep your product fresh and compliant, each tube provides a secure seal that meets child-resistance standards. Say goodbye to misplaced caps—once opened, the lid stays attached, ensuring ease of use and preventing unwanted spills. Whether you're a dispensary owner looking to elevate your packaging game or a personal consumer seeking reliable storage, these tubes offer a powerful combination of safety, freshness, and environmental responsibility.

  • Child-Resistant Compliance: Meets current regulations, ensuring safety and peace of mind.
  • Eco-Friendly Construction: Manufactured with sustainability in mind, reducing your carbon footprint.
  • Simple, Squeezable Design: A quick, hassle-free way to pop the lid without twisting or pushing.
  • Hinged Lids: Lids remain attached, preventing loss or contamination of your product.
  • Opaque Exterior: Helps preserve product freshness and maintain brand confidentiality.
  • Uncompromising Safety: Engineered to comply with strict child-resistant standards, keeping your products out of the wrong hands.
  • Streamlined Access: Users can open the tube with a gentle squeeze, making it convenient for adults while still preventing children from accessing the contents.
  • Eco-Conscious Materials: Align your brand with greener packaging solutions—help protect the planet without sacrificing quality.
  • Professional Brand Image: The opaque finish projects a sleek, modern look, allowing for easy labeling, custom branding, or regulatory messaging.
  • Length: 116mm (ideal for pre-rolls and similar products)
  • Material: High-quality, eco-friendly plastic (opaque finish)
  • Closure Type: Hinged, child-resistant lid
  • Color Options: Standard opaque colors (e.g., black, white, green)
  • Compliance: Meets ASTM and CFR standards for child-resistant packaging
  • Bulk Packaging: Sold in packs or cases (contact us for bulk order details)

Usage Tips:

  • Gently squeeze both sides of the tube near the top to pop the hinged lid open.
  • Ensure the lid is firmly closed after each use to maintain freshness and odor control.
  • For dispensaries, consider adding custom labels or branding wraps for a professional touch.

Additional Info:

  • Shipping options include standard, expedited, and bulk freight.
  • For wholesale inquiries or special branding requests, reach out to our support team.

Ready to upgrade your dispensary or personal storage solutions? Order your 116mm Opaque Child Resistant Tube now and enjoy eco-friendly, compliant packaging that keeps your product fresh and secure!
